What is @SuccinctLabs, and how is it shaping the future of ZK infrastructure?  With the world’s first decentralized prover network now live on mainnet, we sat down with @theedwardli to discuss how Succinct powers verifiable computation for Mantle Network and beyond. https://t.co/n7Hii8EuKB  So what exactly is Succinct?  We kicked things off by asking how the world’s first decentralized prover network works, and why it’s set to play a key role in scaling and securing the next generation of blockchain applications. https://t.co/pLUpdj6eJR  Mantle Network is transitioning to a Validium powered by OP Succinct.  We asked what this means in practice and why integrating validity proofs marks such a significant step forward for scalability, security, and developer experience. https://t.co/xIRVBgEZcX  So what does OP Succinct mean for end users?  From faster withdrawals to lower fees and stronger security, here’s how the upgrade will enhance the everyday experience on Mantle Network. https://t.co/x4k09AsssL  Mantle is building the liquidity chain of the future.  We asked how OP Succinct supports that vision and helps drive capital efficiency, deep liquidity, and high-performance on-chain finance. https://t.co/ixzKXLIrLq  When can users expect OP Succinct to go live on Mantle Network?  We closed by asking about the integration timelines and how the rollout will be phased from testnet to mainnet. https://t.co/ggCL4WdfYm

Mantle Network is excited to welcome two powerhouse leaders from @Bybit_Official as Key Advisors: Helen Liu and Emily Bao.  This marks a major step forward in our ecosystem expansion and realignment. https://t.co/uKkomEXYCI  Helen Liu — Co-CEO of Bybit — joins with deep operational experience, having helped scale Bybit globally across business operations, technology deployment and full regional growth. From Nokia to Microsoft to Bybit — Helen's track record speaks for itself.  Emily Bao, Head of Spot at Bybit and founder of ByReal, has been at the forefront of connecting real-world assets with onchain execution. She brings a sharp eye for ecosystem design and fair market infrastructure.  With Helen and Emily joining Mantle as Key Advisors, we gain:   • Stronger strategic alignment with Bybit  • Executional expertise from CEX to Web3  • Momentum on ecosystem expansion, partnerships, and DeFi innovation  Mantle's next chapter is about pushing boundaries with the best minds in the space.  We're thrilled to have Helen and Emily guiding us forward — starting now.  Let's build.  https://t.co/KvLKSWaGcT
